    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>The Unmatched, Ultimate Idols</strong><br />A starry-eyed and radiant people, bursting with uncontained energy that is extremely contagious. The Oshi are cosmic lights of inspiration to those all around the world, spreading their ideas of happiness and love far and wide to all.</p><p><strong>Oshi Traits</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 to an ability score, +1 to any other ability score. (Recommended: +2 Charisma, +1 Intelligence)</p></li><li><p><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 30 feet.</p></li><li><p><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> You gain 2 skill proficiencies of your choice.</p></li><li><p><strong>Favorite Show:</strong> You know 1 additional D-Rank Oshi Clan Jutsu. This does not count against your jutsu known.</p></li></ul>",
